column2: SELECT TOP #    SpecObj.specObjID,    SpecObj.z,    SpecObj.ra,    SpecObj.dec,    SpecObj.sourceType,   SpecObj.class,   zooSpec.p_el,   zooSpec.p_cw,   zooSpec.p_acw,   zooSpec.p_mg    FROM SpecObj, zooSpec    WHERE zooSpec.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID   AND SpecObj.ra<=#    AND SpecObj.ra>=#    AND SpecObj.dec <=#    AND SpecObj.dec >=#   ORDER BY SpecObj.z DESC
